summary: The healing power of acupuncture is proven by ancient Chinese people for thousands of years, and nowadays is experienced by increasing number of people in the modern world by clinical practice.  Whether you are experiencing physical pains or emotional problems, Bojin Acupuncture aims to provide you a natural, safe and holistic approach to help you to heal, regenerate your innate healing capacity, thus restoring your balance among body, mind and spirit.   We are specialized in the Five Elements acupuncture and Balance Method for treating pains and improve your health. Please contact us at info@bojin.nl, or ring 06 4388 7997 if you wish to discuss treatment or your health concern.
